# Reddit API Configuration
# Get these values from: https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps
# Create a "script" type app and use the provided credentials

REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=your_reddit_client_id_here
REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=your_reddit_client_secret_here
REDDIT_USER_AGENT=script:KafkaSentimentProject:v1.0 (by /u/your_reddit_username)
REDDIT_USERNAME=your_reddit_username
REDDIT_PASSWORD=your_reddit_password

# Database Configuration
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_NAME=sentana
DB_USER=postgres
DB_PASSWORD=password

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env (cp .env.example .env)
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual Reddit API credentials
# 3. Make sure your Reddit app is created with "script" type
# 4. Configure database settings for TimescaleDB/PostgreSQL
# 5. The .env file is already included in .gitignore to protect your credentials